   <body>
      <context>
         <note>Anchoring bolts are not supplied. Use appropriate hardware
for the floor type.</note>
         <table frame="none" outputclass="font:10" pgwide="1">
            <tgroup cols="2">
               <colspec colname="col1" colsep="0"/>
               <colspec colname="col2"/>
               <tbody>
                  <row rowsep="0">
                     <entry>
                        <fig>
                           <image href="../Images/Reality_25-50_kw_upsseismicdetails_w85mm_0000164637.svg"
                                  placement="inline"/>
                        </fig>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <fig>
                           <image href="../Images/Reality_25-50_kw_transformerseismicdetails_w85mm_0000164636.svg"
                                  placement="inline"/>
                        </fig>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <fig>
                           <image href="../Images/Reality_25-50_kw_topcabinetseismicdetails_w85mm_0000164635.svg"
                                  placement="inline"/>
                        </fig>
                     </entry>
                     <entry/>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Drill anchoring holes in the floor according to your system.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Install the rear seismic anchoring bracket(s) on the floor.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Front View</title>
                  <image href="../Images/Reality_25-50_kw_installrearseismictofloor_w120mm_0000164475.svg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Push the cabinet(s) into position against the rear seismic
anchoring brackets.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <fig>
                  <title>Rear View</title>
                  <image href="../Images/Reality_25-50kw_movecabinetintorears_w120mm_0000164474.svg"
                         placement="inline"/>
               </fig>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Save the front seismic anchoring brackets – they
will be installed in <xref href="Final_Installation_0000161963.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
